Reactive Strike: (R) Makes a melee Strike on a foe within reach that uses a manipulate or move action, makes a ranged Strike, or leaves a square while moving
Shed Tail: (R) Can release tail to escape being grabbed and then Stride without triggering reactions from the grabbing creature; regrowth takes 1 day and inflicts -2 Balance
Shield Block: (R) Raised shield negates damage equal to its hardness; self and shield each suffer any remaining damage
Terrain Advantage: Non-lizardfolk foes in difficult terrain or in water without a swim Speed are off-guard vs. self
Threatening Approach: (2) Successful Demoralize after Striding to a spot adjacent to a foe inflicts frightened 2
Vicious Swing: (2) Melee Strike inflicts 1 extra damage die and counts as 2 Strikes for the multiple attack penalty
